pr_body:
Added whitespacing to article and  blocks 
content section modified, 
improvements in left navbar. 
fixed a navbar bug occuring in mobile devices. ( ham burger was hidden due to irregular spacing in navbar)


![whitespace-feature](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/88277883-13d9f780-ccff-11ea-9e8d-9328fbf46114.png)

![content](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/88277924-26543100-ccff-11ea-8c7f-298dba1688b8.png)

@jcayouette @Loquacity Please have a look !

Re designed the error 404 page.
made a svg and added it into img folder.
Made this page responsive to standard device widths.


![error404page](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/88802499-c7902b00-d1c8-11ea-8034-6a77db28a166.png)


@jcayouette @Loquacity Please review it!

Improved the styling of inline buttons, menu and updated warning admon block icon.

Button
![button-macro](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/90015605-73a43c80-dcc6-11ea-879f-37e453720968.png)

 Menu
![menu-macro](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/90015618-79018700-dcc6-11ea-9f51-f717e5b35ebb.png)

Warning Admon Block
![admon-warn](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/90015622-7acb4a80-dcc6-11ea-9796-8f114fcae0a2.png)


@jcayouette @Loquacity  Please have a look

# Description

To select translation, a hover down menu has been added to Navbar. 

![langselfinal](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/89286968-bb94e500-d670-11ea-9015-e57ad29e38ee.png)


@jcayouette @Loquacity Please have a Look!

pr_body:
This PR include:

- Styling Of image Block.

![imageblock](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/90596839-7c889700-e20d-11ea-85a7-080bc029ee0b.png)

- Buttons when encountered on one line after the other were overlapping(few cases only). So padding is fixed to make them look consistent.

![button](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/90596956-bd80ab80-e20d-11ea-8417-d33c7f967bd8.png)

![Screenshot from 2020-08-18 00-32-15](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/90596964-bfe30580-e20d-11ea-9544-25cc767858bc.png)

- asterix icon size decreased and added white-spaces between dlist block.

![asterix](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/90597060-f28cfe00-e20d-11ea-9b85-c63509ce8c97.png)
![aster](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52316491/90597062-f4ef5800-e20d-11ea-9245-5e1707ff8736.png)

- Margin added when any two blocks are encountered one after the other. 

@jcayouette @Loquacity Please review this!
